Subject: [PATCH] regulator: pwm-regulator: Add validity checks in continuous
 .get_voltage
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1218260
